ible population of\nblack holes that are the elusive seeds leading to the formation of supermassive\nblack holes in galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Feb 2017 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 May 2017 00:46:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-10"}
